</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[207,1190,412,949]" pageId="6" pageNumber="53">
des Teppes de Verbois (bord du Rhône), Rus- Fig. 4. 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Illiger" baseAuthorityYear="1807" box="[830,1071,581,602]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphiximorpha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subsessilis">
